pageContext.claim: “We have 49 Democrats. I never see him. The only one I see is crying Chuck. He represents everyone. Bill never calls me and says, you know I'd like to get something from Florida for Florida. Okeechobee, the damn, we're doing that because Rick Scott was driving us all crazy in the White House.”
pageContext.analysis: Nelson may have not "called him" but he did make overtures to the president along with Florida's other senator — Marco Rubio.
